All right , then , '' Hope called back . 
Then she released her hold on the bridles and looked down , in dismay , at her frock and hands , and then up at the three men . 
Before they reached the Palms the sun was out and shining with fierce brilliancy , reflecting its rays on every damp leaf , and drinking up each glistening pool of water . 
They think it's fine ! '' said young Langham , who had run down the hill to tell them about it . 
